                type="place">
               <name xml:id="tag2" type="place">
          Cornwall
        </name>
            </rs>.-<lb/>
- I shall shew a sketch of the<lb/>
spot, &amp; though the minute fact<lb/>
can scarcely be exhibited by means<lb/>
of it; yet the elucidation will<lb/>
be more distinct.-<lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">Instance</hi>.<lb/>
