- Similar circumstances occur,<lb/>
perhaps more distinctly in the<lb/>
Rocks of parallel Stratification;<lb/>
|_And the whole of the Strata of<lb/>
a Country, are often cut through<lb/>
by the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
