their dispositions &amp; ramifications,<lb/>
&amp; that they must deviate in<lb/>
various ways from the perpendiculars,<lb/>
&amp; that they can never be expected<lb/>
rectilinear or equable through<lb/>
the whole of their course. - There<lb/>
